This paper is about medical image segmentation using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of attention mechanisms and multiplexing, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with medical imaging (cs.MM) and the use of contextual information, which is relevant to neural networks (cs.NE).
